---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Filename:       Serial-DataBlast.spin2
    Description:    Simple serial demo that sends all printable characters to the terminal
    Author:         Jesse Burt
    Started:        Jan 5, 2016
    Updated:        Jan 21, 2024
